// Nightly Build by @Keehea918
// Change keybind at "key_press C"

def module Toggle-Anchor
def desc "Press C to place the anchor, then switch to Glowstone, switch to a totem, and use it."

on key_press C if playing switch #anchor then input right then wait 0.04 then switch #glowstone then input right then wait 0.04 then switch #totem then input right
